title: Shaag Chess 3D Game for Windows XP and Vista
description:
Now you can play chess in Windows, in 3D or 2D. Have fun with the rotate-able, tilt-able, scale-able interface. Play against multiple computer opponents, from easy to hard. Helpfully shows moves that are legal, for the learning chess player! Now with multiple chess boards to play on.

XP and Vista Compatible - just download - extract and play. Good 3D chess game.
